          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>ABLE Age Adjustment Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to qualified ABLE programs, to increase the age&nbsp;threshold for eligibility for such programs from 26 to 46. (Tax-favored ABLE [Achieving a Better Life Experience] accounts are designed to enable individuals with disabilities to save for and pay for disability-related expenses.)</p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
